*Nestali* su iz vidokruga nakon što su se okrenuli ulicom. (They disappeared from sight after they turned down the street.)

Čuveni su po tome da su *nestali* bez traga. (They were famous for having disappeared without a trace.)

Susretali smo se još kada su *nestali*. (We were still meeting when they disappeared.)

Nerazjašnjeno je odakle su *nestali*. (It was unclear where they disappeared from.)

Mnogi su verovali da su *nestali*. (Many believed they had disappeared.)